11#ifndef VPX_VP9_COMMON_VP9_MFQE_H_

14#ifdef __cplusplus
15extern "C" {
16#endif
17
18// Multiframe Quality Enhancement.
19// The aim for MFQE is to replace pixel blocks in the current frame with
20// the correlated pixel blocks (with higher quality) in the last frame.
21// The replacement can only be taken in stationary blocks by checking
22// the motion of the blocks and other conditions such as the SAD of
23// the current block and correlated block, the variance of the block
24// difference, etc.
25void vp9_mfqe(struct VP9Common *cm);
26
27#ifdef __cplusplus
28} // extern "C"
29#endif
30
31#endif // VPX_VP9_COMMON_VP9_MFQE_H_
